10 Real-Life AI Applications Used Daily
1.	Google Search
Uses machine learning to rank search results by analyzing keywords, past searches, location, and user behavior.
2.	YouTube Recommendations
ML models study watch history, likes, and viewing time to recommend videos you’re most likely to enjoy.
3.	Google Maps
Uses ML to predict traffic conditions and find the fastest routes based on real-time and historical data.
4.	Instagram Feed & Reels
Machine learning analyzes your interactions (likes, shares, time spent) to personalize your feed.
5.	WhatsApp Spam Detection
ML models detect spam messages by learning patterns from reported and suspicious messages.
6.	Amazon Shopping Suggestions
Uses ML to recommend products based on browsing history, purchases, and similar user behavior.
7.	Netflix Recommendations
Machine learning analyzes viewing history and ratings to suggest movies and series you may like.
8.	Google Assistant / Siri
Uses ML and natural language processing to understand voice commands and give accurate responses.
9.	Gmail Spam Filter
ML models classify emails as spam or important by learning from user actions and message content.
10.	Phone Camera (AI Camera)
Uses ML to recognize scenes, faces, and lighting conditions to automatically enhance photos.
